 use.."Psycho:       "It would be great but then it should be two compos. Sadly.... As to many today are hooked in the Mod2Smp way of tracking and would not get to pleased if they sudenly realizes that they have violated one of the main rules in the compo. But ofcourse, more music compos with different rules would be nice for example The Party as there are so very many contributions there. Two compos are too little today... And to play 20 out of 400 tunes are not to really compete. Some how I think good ones still won't be played."Reflect:      "NOT AT ALL? WHY THE HECK? This is a fine way to get more out of 4 channels and 31 samples!"Wotw:         "Yes!"Xby Dascon (c) Insomnia'98␀